    return "[[Script note.\r- blah blah blah\r- blah blah blah\r]]\r\rTitle: \r	_Screenplay title_\r	Second line\rCredit: written by\rAuthor: \r	Author 1,\r	**Author 2** & Author 3\rSource: script based on...\rNotes: \r	Additional notes (1)\r	Additional notes (2)\rDate: 01/12/2010\rContact:\r	e-mail: email@email.com\r    phone: +12 34 567 89\rCopyright: Licence info\r\r# Act 1: basic blocks\r\r## Sequence 1: scene heading, action, dialogue, parenthetical\r\rINT. BASIC BLOCKS - DAY\r\rAction. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action.\r\rAction. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action.\r\rHERO 1\rBlah blah blah blah.\r\rHERO 2\rBlah blah.\r(parenthetical)\rBlah blah.\r\rAction. action. action. action.\r\r## Sequence 2: boneyard and notes\r\rEXT. BASIC BLOCKS - NIGHT\r\rAction. Action. Action[[ (inline note)]]. Action.\r\r/*\r\rIgnored.\rIgnored. /* nested */\rIgnored.\r\r*/\r\rAction. action. action. action. /*ignored*/action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. action. /*ignored /*nested*/ */action. action. action. action. action. action. action.\r\r[[Long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long...\r\r...multiline note]]\r\r## Sequence 3: Formatting\r\rINT. FORMATTING - DAY\r\rNormal test, _underline test_, *italic test*, **bold test**, ***bold and italic test***, _*underline and italic test*_, _**underline and bold test_**, _***underline, bold and italic test***_.\r\r_Long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long long **(with nested bold)** long long long long underlined text._\r\rEXT. ESCAPING FORMATTING - NIGHT\r\rWhat the f\\*ck! Escape\\_escape\\*escape. \r\r> CENTERED, **BOLD**, _UNDERLINE_ <\r\r> TRANSITION:\r\rPage break test...\r\r===\r\r.FORCED HEADER\r\rAction.\r\r# Act 2: Dialogue\r\rINT. SPLIT DIALOGUE - DUSK\r\rAction.\r\rHERO 1\rBlah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah. Blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah. Blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah.\r\rAction.\r\rINT. DUAL DIALOGUE - NIGHT\r\rAction action.\r\rHERO 1\rBlah!\r\rHERO 2 ^\rBlah!\r\rHERO 3\rBlah?\r\rAction action.\r\r# Act 3: edge cases\r\rINT. LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG LONG SCENE HEADER.\r\rAction.\r\rVERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY VERY LONG NAME\rHello, my name is Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Very Long Name.\r\r# Act 4: Misc\r\r## Latin characters\r\rINT. LATIN TEST - DAWN\r\rLatin characters.\r\rPOLISH\rPchnąć w tę łódź jeża lub osiem skrzyń fig.\r\rGERMAN\rFalsches Üben von Xylophonmusik quält jeden größeren Zwerg.\r\rNORWEGIAN\rBlåbærsyltetøy\r\rSPANISH\rEl pingüino Wenceslao hizo kilómetros bajo exhaustiva lluvia y frío, añoraba a su querido cachorro.\r\r## Forced elements\r\r.WNĘTRZE. FORCED ELEMENTS - NIGHT\r\r!INT. ACTION\r\r@McCABE\r~Happy birthday to you!\r\r> FADE TO GREEN.\r\r## Sections and synopsis\r\r= Section synopsis\r\r### Subsection\r\r= Subsection synopsis\r\r= Additional synopsis\r\rINT. SCENE - DAY\r\r= Scene synopsis\r\rAction.\r\r> THE END.\r";
